page.text: This Brochure of 12 pages I created to give the company TLW Real Estate a new Company Presentation. It has been created in InDesign and the photos have been improved in Photoshop to go well with a strong orange color. The text is light and clean. The brochure was further developed in several languages and ongoing Projects were added when needed.
